    """

    def __init__(self, model: str):
        self.model = model

    def embed_documents(self, texts: List[str]) -> List[List[float]]:
        """Embed search docs."""
        return [[0.5, 0.6, 0.7] for _ in texts]

    def embed_query(self, text: str) -> List[float]:
        """Embed query text."""
        return self.embed_documents([text])[0]
